fixin - indent freely

Automatically convert to and from your vim indentation preferences for files
that have vim modelines. This is especially useful for managing indentation
among multiple contributors with different indentation preferences: not just
tabs vs spaces, but tabs vs 2-spaces, 4-spaces, 8-spaces, and even the silly
people who use 3-spaces.

